  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bcd, \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Stolen petrol, two-wheeler by breaking into a house in Yali",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A house on New Chemmani Road, Jaffna, was broken into early on Wednesday 06th and petrol and a bicycle were stolen.",
        "Yesterday morning, while searching for the two-wheeler in the house, they found that petrol had been stolen from the motorcycle.",
        "After that, when the security camera installed in the house was checked, the thief entered the house and stole the two-wheeler and the petrol from the motorcycle and observed Selvathan."
      ],
